    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Could you rather use the `refine` function of the `searchBox` from the [`renderState`](https://www.algolia.com/doc/api-reference/widgets/render-state/js/#examples)?\r\n\r\nWe don't usually recommend using the helper directly.\r\n\r\nNOTE: for using renderState you will need to update your InstantSearch installation",
